                                <div><span class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500">Dias em atraso (máx.):</span> <span class="font-semibold ${Number(maxOverdueDays || 0) > 0 ? 'text-amber-700' : 'text-gray-600'}">${Number(maxOverdueDays || 0) > 0 ? maxOverdueDays : '&mdash;'}</span></div>
